{"tid":125229,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新樓露台和工作平台分開 網民：低智設計","createTime":"2017-02-18T09:59:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-19T05:10:14.000Z","uid":10540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"23d8fc7ffe803eaad1123b822eb4ac1f38a7c242","tid":125229,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T09:59:43.000Z","msg":"之前黐埋一齊咪好地地，啲泛民, 環團為反對而反對，政府修例咪搞成不輪不類囉<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ps.hket.com/content/1663039\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Fcontent%2F1663039&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaJzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=669a6822\" target=\"_blank\">http://ps.hket.com/content/1663039</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1660000/1663039/tomn20160523018_edit_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1660000%2F1663039%2Ftomn20160523018_edit_600.jpg&h=ec6e350d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hongkongcard.com/webeditor/attached/20120925090949_41399.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongcard.com%2Fwebeditor%2Fattached%2F20120925090949_41399.jpg&h=5ae4f088&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不少新樓盤都會提供露台和工作平台，讓住戶可以曬晾衣服及作休憩之用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-VgCxqXRaaDM/UhDZst5cWcI/AAAAAAAAM_0/Qf890NDOw10/s1600/IMG_5287_01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-VgCxqXRaaDM%2FUhDZst5cWcI%2FAAAAAAAAM_0%2FQf890NDOw10%2Fs1600%2FIMG_5287_01.jpg&h=f886f3a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過，有網民發現，現時的新樓環保露台和工作平台是分開興建，不像10年前左右的新盤，兩者合併成一個大露台，認為現時設計沒有以往的方便，反而令整個單位布局變得奇怪，是「低智」的設計。<br />\n<br />\n除了影響單位格局，更有部分面積極細的工作平台採用推門設計，令「淨係度門佔曬可用空間」，網民質疑係浪費空間，並獲得其他網民一面倒認同。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>網民點睇：</strong><br />\n<br />\nspirixxxx：不就是因為有群「用家」胡亂批評，說合併建築「有違立法原意」，是賺到盡的奸商嗎?<br />\n<br />\nsmal_poxxxx：如果工作平台放左廚房，能與露台形成對流，咁間屋係好通風好好住的。可惜咁好既設計，太小了。依家工作平台多數放在睡房，簡直係阻地方，反而少左衣櫃位<br />\n<br />\nbaxxxx：好地地一個大露台咪幾好用，夾硬拆成兩個細既，不倫不類<br />\n<br />\nVinxxxx：呢種工作平台簡直是香港特色，用來出去吸支煙可以講得過去工咩作？有d 露台和工作平台合併，一邊用鐵欄，一邊用玻璃，真的九唔搭八......"},{"pid":"27d15c602c35942b57342a8e977d7cac33a07464","tid":125229,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T10:08:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲泛民, 環團為反對而反對，政府修例咪搞成不輪不類囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解關佢地事? 佢地話要分開?<br />\n<br />\nSORRY, 無跟開...願聞其詳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ff113d5e0150fd9fed984b09bc39c89c206b968","tid":125229,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T10:30:48.000Z","msg":"反正都買唔起&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eb02c0c1c92343f433fabc75496ae36b2b944ca","tid":125229,"uid":37165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T11:04:51.000Z","msg":"新鴻基啲新樓得300呎都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兩個露台"},{"pid":"03879d80fd88815bd30c6cb6b6e54a06f38bce1f","tid":125229,"uid":52068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T03:16:48.000Z","msg":"話知你起到個地下好似lego咁，反正都唔係攞黎住"},{"pid":"425ca35b4c9610e29f403b59819ac10fb7e5fe33","tid":125229,"uid":40839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T03:30:53.000Z","msg":"屌唔好講啦<br />\n屋企就係呢種設計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n廁所有道門連住個工作平台"},{"pid":"cc22cc0ab5d73b5970f2d897a2454305c59d2efe","tid":125229,"uid":32676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T04:52:42.000Z","msg":"屌on撚9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c38bdccee2c0955b7bb7ea0bbeab6e6604ec2374","tid":125229,"uid":16085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T05:04:11.000Z","msg":"觀月樺峰堆樓咪咁<br />\n<br />\n好耐啦<b